Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,237年的7月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經26歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早季 有人找
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我馬上來
